<p>Today, I visited the <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/Zaporizhzhya?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw"> #Zaporizhzhya&gt; </a>&gt; nuclear power plant to assess the situation after the catastrophic Nova&gt; Kakhovka dam flooding. <a href="https://t.co/TSO5ml0cJa"> pic.twitter.com/TSO5ml0cJa&gt; </a>&gt;&gt; — Rafael MarianoGrossi (@rafaelmgrossi) <a href="https://twitter.com/rafaelmgrossi/status/1669388059656306688?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw"> June 15, 2023&gt; </a></p>
</blockquote>
